----
&gt; Create a 101.conf in /etc/vz/conf | /etc/sysconfig/vz-scripts
vzctl create 101
vzctl set 101 --onboot yes --save
vzctl set 101 --userpasswd root:password
vzctl start 101

See stats on the VM
----
vzctl exec 101 cat /proc/user_beancounters

Check Memory Usage (in MG)
----
vzmemcheck -vA</pre></div><div class="clear"></div><div class="footer">Powered by <a href="http://www.sinatrarb.com/">Sinatra</a>,
